---
// About section component
---

<section id="about" class="bg-strawhat-bg relative py-32 md:py-48">
  <!-- Hat landing spot - decorative element on the right -->
  <div
    data-hat-landing="about"
    class="absolute top-32 right-12 flex size-16 items-center justify-center md:top-40 md:right-20"
  >
    <div class="border-strawhat-red h-3 w-6 rounded-full border-2 opacity-60">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="space-y-12">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2
          class="text-strawhat-text text-4xl/tight font-light tracking-tight md:text-6xl"
        >
          Why choose us
        </h2>
        <p
          class="text-strawhat-text-light max-w-2xl text-lg/relaxed font-light"
        >
          We combine technical expertise with creative problem-solving to
          deliver solutions that make a difference.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-strawhat-text text-xl font-light tracking-tight">
            Clean, maintainable code
          </h3>
          <p class="text-strawhat-text-light text-base/relaxed font-light">
            We write code that's not just functional, but also clean,
            well-documented, and easy to maintain. Your future self will thank
            us.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-strawhat-text text-xl font-light tracking-tight">
            User-focused design
          </h3>
          <p class="text-strawhat-text-light text-base/relaxed font-light">
            Every decision we make is driven by what's best for your users. We
            create experiences that people actually want to use.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-strawhat-text text-xl font-light tracking-tight">
            Modern technology stack
          </h3>
          <p class="text-strawhat-text-light text-base/relaxed font-light">
            We stay current with the latest tools and frameworks, ensuring your
            software is built on a solid, future-proof foundation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-strawhat-text text-xl font-light tracking-tight">
            Transparent communication
          </h3>
          <p class="text-strawhat-text-light text-base/relaxed font-light">
            No surprises, no hidden costs. We keep you informed every step of
            the way and work as an extension of your team.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
